a (PMLVM) run by Labour & Employment Dept. are also not eligible.", "003-listElement": "- Farmers whose economic conditions are good like institutional land holders are not eligible.", "004-listElement": "- All the former & current central / state ministers, lok sabha / rajya sabha members, state legislative assembly members, municipal officers, mayors & head of district panchayats are not eligible.", "005-listElement": "- All the working personnels in various department of central / state govt. offices, retired officers or permanent employees are not eligible. However, multi tasking staff and group D workers can take benefits of Kisan pension scheme.", "006-listElement": "- Income tax payees, doctors, engineers, lawyers, chartered accountants & architects who are indulged in an business are also not eligible."}}